snippet: A deal is played in the same strain at both tables in a match. The two opening leads are identical. What has been the greatest disparity in the number of tricks ever won?
abstract: Phillip Alder Bridge column on deal played during the Jacoby Open Swiss Teams event at the Spring Nationals in Memphis.
